# AWS Price Calculator - Overview

This project is a Streamlit application to estimate AWS service costs and generate spending forecasts.

## Main Files
- [run.py](mdc:run.py): Main script to start the application
- [src/app.py](mdc:src/app.py): Main Streamlit application interface
- [src/aws_services.py](mdc:src/aws_services.py): Functions for AWS service price calculations
- [requirements.txt](mdc:requirements.txt): Project dependencies

## Features
- Cost estimation for 9 different AWS services
- Interactive interface to configure specific parameters for each service
- Cost distribution visualization
- Comparison with current AWS costs via Cost Explorer
- Export of results in JSON format
